_sText:
Havent seen anything like this in CS:S so i made something.

Fy-map, no bombspots or hostages.

Both sides layouts are 100% balanced (just mirrored haha) and are build like real ww1 trench structural systems (except for the kinda short distance between both of em.)

Features adjustable shell-firing artillery for both teams and no-mans-land with very little cover between both sides.

(Bots seem to not understand the concept of trench-warfare.)

A de-version with better looks is coming soon.
